Use-case #1: I want to buy an item.

  Sub-case #1: I want to buy a physical item from someone local to me.

  There is a particular item or set of items that I want to buy from someone near my location.

    Minimal Feature Dependencies:
      * Trader search/list
      * Item search/list

    Future Expectations:
      * Want-to-buy lists
      * Reserve item
      * Contact seller (if allowed by seller)


  Sub-case #2: I want to buy these virtual items.

  Why?
